Class FirstOrderCollectionWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.kb.wrapper.KbObjectWrapper
      • com.cyc.kb.wrapper.KbTermWrapper
        • com.cyc.kb.wrapper.KbCollectionWrapper
          • com.cyc.kb.wrapper.FirstOrderCollectionWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FirstOrderCollection, KbCollection, KbObject, KbObject.KbObjectWithArity, KbTerm

    public abstract class FirstOrderCollectionWrapper
extends KbCollectionWrapper
implements FirstOrderCollection
    An abstract base class for implementing FirstOrderCollections per the decorator pattern. To use, extend this class and implement the wrapped() method to return the wrapped object.
